(yeah, out of cloak)

::Tasmanian Kid::
TK saw the missiles coming, and the disks coming at KitKat. He had to act 
quickly. He shot at the missile heading for him first, then used his jumpjet 
to jump over kitkat and terrorsaur, and took both the ion disks, one in his 
shoulder, the other next to it, and accidentally dropped his gun.. He landed 
on the ground several meters away form KitKat and terrorsaur, holding his 
shoulder.

"AAAAAHHHH!!! I'LL KILL THEM!!!!" he screamed, and sat up. He quickly 
grabbed Injector's gun, and fired up at Manterror.

>they're picking on us now, after we just defend ourselves!  You'll pay for
>that!" he yelled, raising both of his arms, firing one ion disk at KitKat,
>one at Terrorsaur.
>"That'll teach you, ya misfits!"
